data.description: Rambling 1 story home with lower level finished space is ready for new owners. This home offers a cozy living room on the main floor with a wood burning fireplace. 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths and 1st floor laundry with half bath. The lower level was professionally finished with a 4th bedroom with egress window, full bath and large family/game room area awaits! All of this is walking distance to the elementary school and easy access to the highway and shopping. Wonderful Subdivision to plant your roots. Let's schedule your first date with this home.
